\pard\sa200\fs28 Best for: East + north-east Perth participants\par
\pard\sa240\fs36 \b How DYAR helps\b0\par
\pard\sa180\fs22\qc \i [IMAGE: DYAR worker sitting beside participant making a phone call together]\i0\par
\pard\sa200\fs28 Ask us anything. We can:\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Find the right advocate for you\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Make the first call with you\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Translate or read for you\par
